[2.008, "o", "Usage: /Users/avizaguri-macbook/PycharmProjects/claude-projects/.venv/bin/cast <command> [options]\r\n\r\nAvailable commands:\r\n  cast                 Run the demo engine (run_demo.sh) with your demo.cfg\r\n  init                 Scaffold cast-studio demo scripts into your project\r\n  render               Convert an asciinema .cast file to GIF and/or MP4\r\n\r\nRun '/Users/avizaguri-macbook/PycharmProjects/claude-projects/.venv/bin/cast <command> --help' for command-specific help.\r\n"]
